The paper deals with an online classification problem with partial feedback, which is a common problem in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The focus on fairness and statistical constraints suggests that it may fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of statistical analysis and constraints also suggests that it may fall under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). The algorithmic approach and analysis of regret rates suggest that it may fall under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) or information theory (cs.IT).
